---
// Terminal demo component - renders a fake terminal with gh infra plan output
---
<div class="terminal" role="img" aria-label="gh infra plan output showing repository changes">
  <div class="terminal-header">
    <div class="terminal-buttons">
      <span class="terminal-btn close"></span>
      <span class="terminal-btn minimize"></span>
      <span class="terminal-btn maximize"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="terminal-title">Terminal</div>
  </div>
  <pre class="terminal-body" set:html={`<span class="t-prompt">$</span> gh infra plan ./repos/
<span class="t-dim">──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</span>
  <span class="t-yellow">~</span> <span class="t-bold">babarot/my-project</span>
      <span class="t-yellow">~</span> description              <span class="t-dim">My project</span> <span class="t-dim">→</span> <span class="t-bold">My awesome project</span>
      <span class="t-green">+</span> topics                   <span class="t-green">[go, cli]</span>
      <span class="t-yellow">~</span> allow_squash_merge       <span class="t-dim">false</span> <span class="t-dim">→</span> <span class="t-bold">true</span>
      <span class="t-yellow">~</span> auto_delete_head         <span class="t-dim">false</span> <span class="t-dim">→</span> <span class="t-bold">true</span>
      <span class="t-red">-</span> wiki                     <span class="t-red">true</span>

  <span class="t-green">+</span> <span class="t-bold">babarot/new-project</span>  <span class="t-green">(new)</span>
      <span class="t-green">+</span> visibility               <span class="t-green">public</span>
      <span class="t-green">+</span> topics                   <span class="t-green">[go, tools]</span>

<span class="t-dim">──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</span>
Plan: <span class="t-bold">1</span> to create, <span class="t-bold">1</span> to update, <span class="t-bold">0</span> to destroy
To apply, run: <span class="t-bold">gh infra apply</span>`} />
</div>

<style>
  .terminal {
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    width: 100%;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  /* Dark theme (default) */
  .terminal-header {
    background: #1a1b27;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #292e42;
  }
  .terminal-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .terminal-btn {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .terminal-btn.close { background: #f7768e; }
  .terminal-btn.minimize { background: #e0af68; }
  .terminal-btn.maximize { background: #9ece6a; }
  .terminal-title {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    color: #565f89;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-right: 44px;
  }
  .terminal-body {
    background: #16161e;
    color: #a9b1d6;
    padding: 24px 24px 32px;
    margin: 0;
    border: none;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, 'SF Mono', Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .terminal-body :global(.t-prompt) { color: #7aa2f7; font-weight: bold; }
  .terminal-body :global(.t-green) { color: #9ece6a; }
  .terminal-body :global(.t-red) { color: #f7768e; }
  .terminal-body :global(.t-yellow) { color: #e0af68; }
  .terminal-body :global(.t-dim) { color: #565f89; }
  .terminal-body :global(.t-bold) { color: #c0caf5; font-weight: bold; }

  /* Light theme */
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-header {
    background: #e1e2e7;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #c4c8da;
  }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-title {
    color: #8990b3;
  }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-body {
    background: #d5d6db;
    color: #343b58;
  }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-body :global(.t-prompt) { color: #2e7de9; }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-body :global(.t-green) { color: #587539; }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-body :global(.t-red) { color: #f52a65; }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-body :global(.t-yellow) { color: #8c6c3e; }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-body :global(.t-dim) { color: #8990b3; }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal-body :global(.t-bold) { color: #343b58; font-weight: bold; }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .terminal {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
</style>
